/wiki/Yoanka_Gonz\u00e1lez: Yoanka González Pérez ( born 9 January 1976 in Villa Clara ) is a Cuban racing cyclist , competing in both road cycling and track cycling . She was the 2004 scratch cycling world champion . She is also married to cyclist Pedro Pablo Pérez
